---
title: Smoky Cheesy Bean Pie with Butternut Squash and Salad
description: Our Smoky Cheesy Bean Pie is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R43_W30_UK_V21328-4_Main_low-e231ebf3.jpg
